<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Il <strong>complemento oggetto</strong> è chiamato anche complemento diretto perché si collega al verbo direttamente, senza preposizioni;</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>risponde alle domande: <strong>chi? / che cosa?</strong> → <em>Facciamo (che cosa?) una festa?</em> → <em>Invitiamo (chi?) gli amici!</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter syntagm-divider" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      <span>Dividi la frase in sintagmi e sottolinea <span class="text-red-600">predicato<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>, <span class="text-blue-600">soggetto<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e <span class="text-green-600">complemento oggetto<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-green-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Eleonora / ha disegnato / un orso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• D'estate<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il sole</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">asciuga</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">i panni</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Stasera<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">porto</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">del gelato</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>alle<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>fragole.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">Prendi</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">la tovaglia</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>di<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>cotone<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>a<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>quadri.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">Filippo</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">ha invitato</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">Luigi</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>alla<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>festa.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">Franca</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">mandò</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span><span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="green" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">dei fiori</span><span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="true" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>a<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>sua<span class="hover:bg-blue-50 hover:px-1 transition" data-syntagm-divider-target="divider" data-correct="false" data-action="click->syntagm-divider#toggleDivider"> </span>madre.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Completa le frasi con un complemento oggetto adatto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Samuele raccoglie</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Guardiamo</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Linda guida</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Quando porterai</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Indica con X le frasi che contengono un complemento oggetto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_1" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Ieri è venuto Pietro con un amico.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_2" value="yes" data-correct-answer="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Può dirmi il prezzo della maglietta?</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_3" value="yes" data-correct-answer="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Questa strada attraversa gli Appennini.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_4" value="yes" data-correct-answer="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Per cena ordinerei delle pizze.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_5" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Giovanni è stato qui?</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_6" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">La statua fu scolpita da Michelangelo.</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">4</span>
      Qual è l'unica frase senza complemento oggetto?
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="A" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Balliamo un tango sulle note di un vecchio disco.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="B" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Emily impara ogni giorno cose nuove.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="C" data-correct-answer="C" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Su un albero del giardino si è nascosto uno scoiattolo.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="D" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Chi vuole una fetta di torta al limone?</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
